Kalahari Resources Plans to List Within Next Two Years, Business Day Says

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-05-19T05:28:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-19/kalahari-resources-plans-to-list-within-next-two-years-business-day-says.html
Kalahari Resources (Pty) Ltd. plans
to list within two years and diversify its mineral interests
into iron ore and chrome, Business Day reported, citing Chairman
Daphne Mashile-Nkosi.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  